'''Aero VIP''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] [[regional airline]] headquartered in [[Portimão]] , Western [[Algarve]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aerovip.pt/en/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105173433/http://aerovip.pt/en/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2013-11-05 |title=Aero Vip - Air Transport Services & Aerial Work Operations - Home |publisher=Aerovip.pt |date= |accessdate=2014-08-13 }}</ref> It operates minor domestic routes within Portugal and also offers additional aviation services.
==History== Aero Vip integrated the 7 Air Group, becoming part of one of the biggest aeronautical groups operating in Portugal and increasing its services. Aero Vip is a company within the aeronautical market that provides the following services: Air Transportation (Regional and Non-Regular), Air Work, Flight Instruction, License Revalidation, Type Rating and Aircraft Rental.{{citation needed|date=August 2016}}
