'''Agustín Edwards Ross''' (February 17, 1852 – November 1, 1897) was a [[Chile]]an businessman and politician.  Edwards served as the [[List of Presidents of the Senate of Chile|President of the Senate of Chile]] from 1893 through 1895.  
