{{notability|date=December 2009}} The '''Rainton Bridge Business Park''' is a [[business park]] located in [[Houghton le Spring]] in the [[City of Sunderland]], [[UK]].
The site is home to a number of well known companies including TRW, Tackle, PCI Services and TNT.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.raintonbridge.com/occupiers/overview.html |title=Rainton Bridge Occupiers |accessdate=2010-08-03}}</ref>
