The '''Union des industries et métiers de la métallurgie''' (Union of Metallurgies Industries or '''UIMM''') is the largest sub-federation of the ''[[Mouvement des Entreprises de France|Mouvement des Entreprises de France (MEDEF)]]'', the [[France|French]] largest [[union of employers]].
Its current president is [[Frédéric Saint-Geours]], who was elected the 20 December 2007.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.lexpansion.com/economie/actualite-economique/le-patron-de-peugeot-succede-a-denis-gautier-sauvagnac-a-la-tete-de-l-uimm_137450.html | title=Le patron de Peugeot succède à Denis Gautier-Sauvagnac à la tête de l'UIMM |publisher=l'Expansion | date=2007-12-20 | accessdate=2008-05-02}}</ref>
